To switch between eth0/wlan0 network interfaces and between static IP and DHCP:
   Edit and copy the appropriate /etc/network/interfaces.* file
    to /etc/network/interfaces
   Enable or disable the dhcpcd service:
      # systemctl enable dhcpcd   (for DHCP)
      # systemctl disable dhcpcd   (for static IP)
      # shutdown -r now
